official_title: An original resolution authorizing the printing of the report entitled "The Cost of Clean Air and Water" as a Senate document.

summary.text: Authorizes the printing of the annual report of the Administrator of the Environmental Protection Agency to the Congress entitled "The Cost of Clean Air and Water" as a Senate document. Directs the printing of 500 additional copies of such document for the use of the Senate Committee on Environment and Public Works.
